{"TopicId":153628,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Where to buy KSP?","CreatedByName":"Planemaster","CreatedById":172611,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T09:47:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Planemaster","CreatedById":172611,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T09:47:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve played the demo which I found pretty fun (gotten to the mun and back \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E) and I\u0027d like to get the full version. Where should I buy it from? I can get it from Steam for \u00A329.99 (\u003Ca href=\u0022http://store.steampowered.com/app/220200/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://store.steampowered.com/app/220200/\u003C/a\u003E) or the KSP website for \u00A310.19 (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/kspstore/index.php?p=22\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalspaceprogram.com/kspstore/index.php?p=22\u003C/a\u003E).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any difference between the two as one is \u00A320 cheaper?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, hope to be \u003Cs\u003Eflying\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0crashing soon\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dangerhamster","CreatedById":146944,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T12:03:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I bought from the store, only practical difference to Steam is the update process. Steam will auto update the game whereas the store version needs you to actively get the update from your account on the store.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T12:06:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222890653\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153611\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481938013\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome! Great devnotes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I feel good inside. Just bought the game for a friend.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn sale for $13.59 on\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/kspstore/index.php?p=22\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ehttps://kerbalspaceprogram.com/kspstore/index.php?p=22\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0until Jan 6.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T12:09:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep, as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/160462-james-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022160462\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/160462-james-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@James Kerman\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0quoted me it\u0027s on sale on the official site. You can get a steam key.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T12:42:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222890991\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153628\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481976596\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can get a steam key.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor new purchases no, you can\u0027t. Refer to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/en/?page_id=19\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EFAQ\u003C/a\u003E:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/en/?page_id=19#0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EI bought the game on the KSP Store, but I want it on Steam. Will you give me a Steam Key?\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn general no. The option to transfer KSP Store licenses to Steam is only available for those who bought KSP before it originally came out on Steam, March 20th 2013.\u00A0Note that if you do qualify for a transfer and choose to do it, the process is OPTIONAL and IRREVERSIBLE. If you transfer your purchase to Steam, you will no longer be able to download or update the game from the KSP Store.\u00A0To move to Steam, log in to your KSP Store profile and you will find the button to start the process next to your download link. If you can\u2019t see the button in your profile it means you purchased the game after it was on Steam and you are not eligible, no exceptions, please don\u2019t insist.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T13:07:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222891008\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153628\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481978579\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stibbons\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, stibbons said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor new purchases no, you can\u0027t. Refer to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/en/?page_id=19\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EFAQ\u003C/a\u003E:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs in you can purchase a Steam key off of kerbalspaceprogram.com for the sale price, which I did. It worked perfectly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T13:12:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry, I thought you were trying to answer \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s question.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Planemaster","CreatedById":172611,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T15:34:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo if I buy it from the website, I have to manually update as opposed to the automatic updates by steam? That\u0027s it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starman4308","CreatedById":122674,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-17T16:41:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222891175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153628\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481988885\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022172611\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Planemaster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Planemaster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo if I buy it from the website, I have to manually update as opposed to the automatic updates by steam? That\u0027s it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBlessing and a curse at times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you start modding, with Steam, you\u0027re going to want to copy your KSP folder so Steam doesn\u0027t auto-update and break your mods to tiny little twigs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}